org.apache.distributedlog.common.annotations

Annotation Type DistributedLogAnnotations.Compression


  • public static @interface DistributedLogAnnotations.Compression
    Annotation to specify the occurrence of a compression operation. These are CPU intensive and should be avoided in low-latency paths.
